  m_text: 'Doctor: States an honest subject, lying subject and a ghost. If lying,
    will call a ghost a lying subject and a lying subject a ghost


    Alchemist:
    States if they are next to at least one lying subject. Could be one ghost and
    one subject, or two subjects


    ALL GHOSTS: Disguises as a random subject
    and gives false information


    Phantom: A subject next to me lies


    Nuckelavee:
    Subjects next to me lie'
